Klopp: &quot;I am absolutely delighted.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It was clear that we needed to be patient, not to get disappointed - we had to do the right things always, again and again and again.&quot;

Klopp on the use of Moreno last season: &quot;I felt that it was unfair at the end of the season. I thought &lsquo;damn, we didn&rsquo;t use him often enough'. Before this season I told him we&rsquo;d be getting another full-back but that we didn&rsquo;t plan on using Milly in the full-back race again.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp on Moreno: &quot;So I said &lsquo;you decide what happens&rsquo;. He&rsquo;s decided it. He&rsquo;s now a much better defender. He&rsquo;s a brilliant footballer. When you see him shooting here you think &lsquo;he can&rsquo;t shoot&rsquo;. He shoots like crazy (in training), it&rsquo;s unbelievable how good he is at it.&quot;
